T04TD3965E:235b-1: bo dhi sa tva go tsa ra pa ri shu ddhi s'u tr'a rtha sam gra ha /
T04TD3965E:235b-3: byang chub sems dpa' spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i mdo'i don mdor bsdus pa /
T04TD3965E:235b-4: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
T04TD3965E:235b-5: mtha' dag spyod yul ma yin pa //
T04TD3965E:235b-6: spyod yul spyod yul min spangs pas //
T04TD3965E:235b-7: spyod yul thams cad dag gyur pa //
T04TD3965E:235b-9: zhing ni yongs su sbyong 'dod pas //
T04TD3965E:235b-10: rang dang gzhan gyi rgyud dag la //
T04TD3965E:235b-11: byang chub sems dpas 'di ltar yid //
T04TD3965E:235b-12: so so'i spyod yul 'gyur bar bya //
T04TD3965E:235b-13: thog mar gnyid sad de yi tshe //
T04TD3965E:235b-14: 'di ltar yid la bya ba ni //
T04TD3965E:235b-15: bsod nams ye shes mngon 'phel don //
T04TD3965E:235b-16: 'bad pa med par mkhas gyur cig / bag med gnyid las rnam grol zhing //
T04TD3965E:235b-17: skye dgu'i mi shes mtshan mo zad //
T04TD3965E:235b-18: thams cad mkhyen pa'i nyi shar bzhin //
T04TD3965E:235b-19: bla med de mthong ldan par shog / gnyid yongs su sad pa yi'o //
T04TD3965E:235b-20: ldang tshe nyon mongs nyer len gyi //
T04TD3965E:235b-21: 'khor ba'i gnas mal spangs nas ni //
T04TD3965E:235b-22: de bzhin gshegs pas brnyes de ltar //
T04TD3965E:235b-23: stobs dang brtson sogs bla med shog / gnas mal las yongs su ldang ba'i'o //
T04TD3965E:235b-24: ngo tsha dang ni khrel yod gos //
T04TD3965E:235b-25: byams dang snying rje'i ska rags ni //
T04TD3965E:235b-26: sems can thams cad bla med par //
T04TD3965E:235b-27: rgyal ba ji bzhin gyon gyur cig / smad g-yogs gyon pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:235b-28: byams chen dang ni brtse ba'i gos //
T04TD3965E:235b-29: bde gshegs ji bzhin gyon pa dang //
T04TD3965E:235b-30: mtha' dag sems can yan lag ni //
T04TD3965E:235b-31: legs spas mnyam pa nyid gyur cig / stong g-yogs gyon pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:235b-32: bla med theg pa chen por ni //
T04TD3965E:235b-33: rkang pa 'jug par byed gyur cig / lha yi bzhon dang tshangs pa yi //
T04TD3965E:235b-34: bzhon pa la sogs nges 'byung gi //
T04TD3965E:235b-35: rim pas mthar gyis bgrod par shog / mchi la lha ma gyon pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:235b-36: lus can thams cad thams cad du //
T04TD3965E:235b-38: thams cad mkhyen pa'i grong khyer gnas //
T04TD3965E:235b-39: sgo chen po ni 'byed par shog / sgo dbye ba'i'o //
T04TD3965E:235b-40: khams gsum rmongs pa chen po yi //
T04TD3965E:235b-41: srid pa'i khyim las phyir byung ste //
T04TD3965E:236a-2: 'jig rten mtha' dag nges 'gro shog / khang pa las phyir 'byung ba'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-3: mi khom ngan 'gro'i g-yang sa las //
T04TD3965E:236a-4: mtha' dag skye bo rnams kyi sgo //
T04TD3965E:236a-5: mi dge gang byas byang sems dang //
T04TD3965E:236a-6: sangs rgyas kyis kyang bcad gyur cig / sgo 'gegs pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-7: bla med de bzhin gshegs pa yi //
T04TD3965E:236a-8: gom pas thams cad du bgrod shog /'gro ba'i 'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-9: nyon mongs ngan du spyod pa yi //
T04TD3965E:236a-10: bshang gci dri ma 'dor gyur cig / dri ma 'dor pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-11: mi gtsang dri ma'i zhing sogs 'dor //
T04TD3965E:236a-12: tshul khrims 'chal ba'i dri bsal te //
T04TD3965E:236a-13: brtse dang bya ba dag pa yi //
T04TD3965E:236a-14: phyag zhabs sems can ldan gyur cig / khrus kyi'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-15: rnam par thar pa'i sgo nas sgor //
T04TD3965E:236a-16: rnam 'phel bde bar gshegs pa bzhin //
T04TD3965E:236a-17: kun mkhyen tshul khrims dri zhim dang //
T04TD3965E:236a-18: ye shes snang ba 'char bar shog / kha 'khru ba dang so shing za ba'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-19: rtag tu sems can mnyam par ni //
T04TD3965E:236a-20: na rgas nyon mongs thams cad dang //
T04TD3965E:236a-21: bral zhing thams cad mtshungs par yang //
T04TD3965E:236a-22: rdo rje snying po'i lus su shog / sman nye bar spyod pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-23: kun nas rab tu dang ba dang //
T04TD3965E:236a-24: 'dod chags la sogs rdul spangs te //
T04TD3965E:236a-25: sems can rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bzhin //
T04TD3965E:236a-26: blta bas mi ngoms skur gyur cig / chag chag dang phyag dar skyang nul gyi'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-27: spyi gtsug 'jig rten mi mthong dang //
T04TD3965E:236a-28: lha dang mi la sogs rnams kyi //
T04TD3965E:236a-29: phyag 'os rtag tu sems can kun //
T04TD3965E:236a-30: rdzogs sangs mchod rten bzhin mchod shog / mchod rten la phyag byed pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-31: skyes bu chen po seng ge yi //
T04TD3965E:236a-33: 'os su gyur pa'i sems can gyi //
T04TD3965E:236a-34: bdud stobs stobs las rgyal thob shog / stan dang gding ba'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-35: kun mkhyen dam chos thams cad kyi //
T04TD3965E:236a-37: skye bo rnams kyis bka' lung ni //
T04TD3965E:236a-38: tshangs dbyangs lta bu thob par shog //
T04TD3965E:236a-39: glegs bam 'byed pa dang 'don pa la sogs pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236a-40: rdul dang nad kyi skyon spangs te //
T04TD3965E:236a-41: gser gyi mdog can gnyen nyid dang //
T04TD3965E:236a-42: sna tshogs yan lag mtshan nyid bzang //
T04TD3965E:236a-43: sems can rgyal ba ji bzhin shog / bla med rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi spyan //
T04TD3965E:236a-44: dag pa lnga dang rtag ldan zhing //
T04TD3965E:236a-45: nyon mongs gdung ba dri ma'i tshogs //
T04TD3965E:236b-0: lus can rnams ni dag par shog / dri la phyis @236b dang spyan 'byed dang khrus la sogs pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236b-1: lam gyi yan lag brgyad ldan chus //
T04TD3965E:236b-2: yun ring zug rngur bying phyung ste //
T04TD3965E:236b-3: chos shes mngon par dag byed dpal //
T04TD3965E:236b-4: lus can rnams kyis rnyed par shog / khrus bya ba sbyin pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236b-5: ma lus bkres dang skom pa las //
T04TD3965E:236b-6: bde gshegs bzhin du rnam grol dang //
T04TD3965E:236b-7: ye shes bdud rtsis legs tshim zhing /
T04TD3965E:236b-8: sems can rnams ni nad med gyur //
T04TD3965E:236b-9: bza' ba dang btung ba la longs spyod pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236b-10: kun mkhyen ye shes spyod pa yis //
T04TD3965E:236b-11: kha mgrin dpal ni brgyan pa dang //
T04TD3965E:236b-12: mi gnas mya ngan 'das par ni //
T04TD3965E:236b-13: shes brtse'i gom pas rim bgrod shog / lung bstan rnam pa bzhi dag dang //
T04TD3965E:236b-14: so sor yang dag rig rnam bzhi //
T04TD3965E:236b-15: pha rol phyin pa chen po'i lam //
T04TD3965E:236b-16: bzhon pa chen por 'dzeg par shog / brtse dang shes rab yang dag 'byung //
T04TD3965E:236b-17: ma lus lus dang ngag gi las //
T04TD3965E:236b-18: gzhan don phyir mi ldog par ni //
T04TD3965E:236b-19: sems can thams cad mnyam gyur cig / tam po la za ba dang //
T04TD3965E:236b-25: thams cad du ni sgrib bral gyi //
T04TD3965E:236b-26: dran dang shes rab yon tan ldan //
T04TD3965E:236b-27: sems can thams cad don phyir yang //
T04TD3965E:236b-28: sems can kun dge byed gyur cig / de dang de'i spyod yul gyi sgo'i rnam pa'o //
T04TD3965E:236b-29: bla med de bzhin gshegs pa yi ni tshul khrims dri //
T04TD3965E:236b-30: byang chub yan lag me tog mdzes khebs de yan lag / bzang po'i mtshan rnams kyis ni mngon par brgyan pa dang //
T04TD3965E:236b-31: sems can rnams ni 'gro ba'i don 'dod gyur par shog / dri 'am bdug pa dang me tog dang rgyan byin pa'i 'o ;
T04TD3965E:236b-32: / grang dang tsha ba'i gdung bsel bar byed pa'i dri zhim dang //
T04TD3965E:236b-33: gdugs dang 'dra ba'i phyogs kyi gnas yangs bdag po dang //
T04TD3965E:236b-34: chos kyi rgyal mtshan bsgreng bas phyogs su brgyan pa yis //
T04TD3965E:236b-35: sems can rnams ni 'gro la rab tu gsal gyur cig / me tog dang gdugs dang rgyal mtshan dang ba dan bsgreng pa'i'o //
T04TD3965E:236b-36: shes rab tu gsal bas mun pa rnam bcom zhing //
T04TD3965E:236b-37: des ni sdig pa'i snum dang sdong bu bsregs nas ni //
T04TD3965E:236b-38: spyan lngar nye bar 'phel ba rnams ni thob pa dang //
T04TD3965E:236b-39: rgyal ba lta bur sems can rnams ni rab gsal shog / de bzhin gshegs pa bla na med pa mi 'gyur pa'i //
T04TD3965E:237a-1: legs pa'i yid ches ngag dag dang //
T04TD3965E:237a-2: tshangs dbyangs ltar 'gyur de dag yon tan chen po ni //
T04TD3965E:237a-3: sems can bde bar gshegs pa dag dang mtshungs gyur cig / sgron ma dang bstod pa 'bal ba'i'o //
T04TD3965E:237a-4: 'gro ba khyab par rgyun chags min //
T04TD3965E:237a-5: mtha' dag smon lam chen po rnams//
T04TD3965E:237a-6: rgyun chad med 'das brtse ba yi //
T04TD3965E:237a-7: mal bder lhag par nyal gyur cig / ma smad spyod pas thams cad du //
T04TD3965E:237a-8: pha rol sems can rjes 'dzin des //
T04TD3965E:237a-9: rang tshul spyod dang spyod yul ni //
T04TD3965E:237a-10: sems can sangs rgyas bzhin gyur cig //
T04TD3965E:237a-11: smon lam dang gnas mal dang ma smad pa'i spyod pa thams cad kyi'o //
T04TD3965E:237a-12: spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i mdo'i don mdor bsdus pa /
T04TD3965E:237a-13: slob dpon dpal sgra gcan 'dzin bzang po'i zhabs kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T04TD3965E:237a-15: // / dpal chos kyi rje sa'i steng na 'gran zla dang bral ba kha che sh'akya shr'i bzang po dang //
T04TD3965E:237a-16: lo ts'a ba byams pa'i dpal gyis bsgyur ba'o /
